{"tid":1298010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非回合］遊行口號嗌多啲五大訴求！","createTime":"2019-07-08T17:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T00:38:22.000Z","uid":76297,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"895c434806cad42da6007e3dece10e2c3300f788","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:47:08.000Z","msg":"最近好多遊行活動，但大家都好多時間會嗌「香港人，加油！」<br />\n而忽略左<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時會帶頭嗌五大訴求，但相比下「香港人，加油」又多人知又易跟，所以五大訴求既聲音好似比較薄弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此！係時候諗下點樣可以令多啲人一齊嗌五大訴求啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拋磚</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>簡易化五大訴求</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n撤回惡法 <br />\n撤銷控罪<br />\n沒有暴動 只有暴政<br />\n追究黑警<br />\n<br />\n呢啲就遊行都有聽過既口號覺得都比較易嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>印多啲五大訴求舉牌或者banner</strong></span><br />\n已家遊行比較少見到五大訴求既海報<br />\n有時啲人想跟都未必跟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有啲簡化啲既字句既舉牌banner咁就方便大家跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗下可以點令五大訴求既聲音大啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係個句，兄弟爬山<br />\n做咩都好一齊努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n少出post出得唔好屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例 <br />\n二、收回暴動定義 <br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"fa1bc2f22d941f6d7d6c110717b0d4ba135eb4aa","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"撤回惡法！"},{"pid":"e3327a31ed0dda9471eb8df2ed6a34c593b655c1","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:49:00.000Z","msg":"撤銷控罪！"},{"pid":"d68e8cc9027fb5bf8e3cc220c50f8a168bd939b8","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"沒有暴動 只有暴政！"},{"pid":"f07b9d63793054984614a48e4b31afb5e1c91db2","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"追究黑警！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807ef1d5db67b09f955f2e0961c2b815ff3bd352","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"立即實行雙真普選！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bae9ec96081e4fcb281383dadd1926065278130","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"撤回！ 惡法！"},{"pid":"caccb61daa88c4573b5a8439f7163d9064551c82","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:51:05.000Z","msg":"撤銷！ 控罪！"},{"pid":"45914ce751080f0924b6fa239780f7f3644d47fb","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"釋放！ 義士！"},{"pid":"2d6a10a26a1356aa8e4e1af4173b3e8f2153305a","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:53:50.000Z","msg":"不分化！不割蓆！"},{"pid":"95a70ff1557701d6fb734d0ffbc7beabb6de4555","tid":1298010,"uid":76297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:54:46.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5df37ed66